{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "cbed35ae-b714-4cac-9a62-3dc607391d4e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 890.3662298828126,
      "y": 350.6250018554688,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "ES6",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0337930b-f319-4a6d-a3d4-c9f969466135",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1310.3662298828126,
      "y": -18314.457619227152,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "let",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "35e29116-e6e4-4324-9766-b2ef7cfc340b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -18997.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "概念",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "cc05eddc-939e-4f04-8c98-11b35446582b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -18997.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "块级作用域",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3529c65d-11ed-4849-aa06-efb927b307f6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -18997.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "块级作用域表示的是定义的变量可执行上下文环境只能在一个代码块中，一个代码块由一个大括号括住的代码构成，超出这个代码块范围将无法访问内部的变量",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "72a1de38-55ce-42f8-a490-16a1b3c9e931",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -18389.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "特点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6a907155-1c4e-4d09-95d0-1c9794754e83",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -18837.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "块级作用域",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f3133f18-29aa-458a-8398-768cabfb36dd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -18677.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "无变量提升",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "72ea350a-6c97-4b28-830b-f1e44358d9fd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -18437.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "存在暂时性死区",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "147869ab-6808-4feb-8090-626c0ccd9f94",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -18517.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在使用let声明变量之前，该变量都是不可访问的",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "2a65831e-2ae5-429b-a051-0fb20d471ae7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -18357.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在let定义的变量之前使用typeof运算符同样会抛出异常",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f1017587-4c22-4161-8fae-4e09ee4067b1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -18357.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "针对非let或const声明的变量，使用typeof运算符确实是绝对安全的，处理一个未声明的变量时会返回“undefined”",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3eccf1d4-108b-4cde-8ca1-827fc3f18533",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -18117.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不能重复声明",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "79739af9-7618-416d-bbbc-91300ca40e5d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -18197.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在同一个作用域内，不能使用let重复声明相同的变量",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "168c2eba-1401-4c8a-afba-c413d02e8cd1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -18037.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在函数内部，如果处于相同作用域下，则不能重复声明和形参相同的变量名",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ab561f10-802f-46a8-a543-0358b14d5db8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -17877.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "全局作用域声明的变量不是window对象的属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8c64b92f-6676-4aa6-9d77-ea7b1fb73317",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -17557.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "优点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0ea9854d-eaf5-4875-94c9-2197abb4dabb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -17717.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不会导致for循环索引值泄露",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3fae7a89-be5e-49c4-97e6-0613a1242465",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -17557.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "避免出现变量提升导致的变量覆盖问题",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "aab64a93-3544-43ea-9f0a-8ae53a04188d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -17557.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "var arg1 = 'kingx';\nfunction foo() {\n\n    console.log(arg1);  // undeﬁned\n\n    if (false) {\n\n        var arg1 = 'kingx2';\n\n    }\n\n}\n\nfoo(); // undeﬁned",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9e434988-398b-48df-ba92-f9755041027a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -17397.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "代替立即执行函数IIFE",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "24c2a73a-79b5-492e-854c-a92123b60256",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -17397.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "立即执行函数的内部是一个独立的函数级作用域，使用IIFE的目的主要是避免污染当前作用域内的变量，而使用块级作用域则可以直接避免这个问题",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7d463516-d2a1-40b1-b5c8-0b624f9de09b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1310.3662298828126,
      "y": -16917.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "const",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "96a1c31f-2ccf-44a6-abad-1e9daf29a43f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -17237.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "使用const声明的值为一个常量，一旦声明将不会再改变",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3d1b1316-5cc2-491b-88b3-5ed810d790d0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -17077.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在块级作用域内有效",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f084e6bd-acbd-40f3-b41b-599a2c1dc331",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -16917.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不存在变量提升，会产生暂时性死区",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "02f2af56-9de2-4699-aa03-0bee2df82bc7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -16757.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不能重复声明变量",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a3b44c30-94bc-4b20-a426-96654cc72ed8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -16597.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "全局作用域声明的变量不是window对象的属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f49e2813-117f-4892-9546-5c6e92ff59a2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1310.3662298828126,
      "y": -15597.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "解构赋值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9f2e461f-9d01-40ca-a7c8-6cdc9abb79a6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -16037.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "数组",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c1ac0db2-a0ce-48e7-876c-e672a181e2e4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -16437.124285893817,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "数组在解构赋值时，使用的是模式匹配，只要等号两边数组的模式相同，右边数组的值就会相应赋给左边数组的变量",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "849323ee-1374-420f-b541-b36870e98d5c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -16277.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "数组解构默认值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0c26fdde-3293-4d4b-ae6b-1cabc4f3e200",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -16277.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "let [num1 = 1, num2] = [, 34];\nconsole.log(num1); // 1\n\nconsole.log(num2); // 34",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "36f7d8f1-42d8-4f8d-8351-0b7116bacf47",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -16117.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "交换变量",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "aba41e05-49d5-4c80-a83e-039f5bb47ffc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -16117.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "var a = 1;\nvar b = 2;\n\n// 使用数组的解构赋值交换变量\n\n[b, a] = [a, b];",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9f19ba89-bc1a-4b90-a98b-035a6b45cd94",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -15957.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "解析函数返回的数组",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "68931f0f-07cb-4da9-943a-80bc9d26e255",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -15957.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "function fn() {\n    return [12, 34];\n\n}\n\nlet [num1, num2] = fn();\n\nconsole.log(num1); // 12\n\nconsole.log(num2); // 34",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "16475429-ff5a-413e-bc20-90e1283b73aa",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -15797.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "嵌套数组的解构",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b9d6977e-a26c-43f7-9173-bb940b850bc2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -15797.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "let [num1, num2, [num3]] = [12, [34, 56], [78, 89]];\n\nconsole.log(num1); // 12\n\nconsole.log(num2); // [34, 56]\n\nconsole.log(num3); // 78",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "599a52ce-4549-4c0a-b17a-b3d640142d96",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -15637.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "函数参数解构",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9ba79001-ba93-4c2c-8579-e9a2a31c1f55",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -15637.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "function foo([arg1, arg2]) {\n    console.log(arg1); // 2\n\n    console.log(arg2); // 3\n\n}\n\nfoo([2, 3]);",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ae73817c-8c4c-41ed-9f1f-ad5c83751701",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -15157.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a14814c5-514c-4832-a99d-bd3db4d7bfbd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -15477.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "对象在解构赋值时，右侧解构对象的属性名和左侧定义对象的变量名必须相同，这样才可以进行解构",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "15b17c7a-7d32-46d9-a734-b558956b82c3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -15317.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "对象解构的默认值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "90fb4604-21a7-457a-b221-fd408fb12953",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -15317.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "let {m, n = 1, o = true} = {m: ‘kingx’, o: null};\nconsole.log(m); // kingx\n\nconsole.log(n); // 1\n\nconsole.log(o); // null，因为null与undeﬁned不严格相等，默认值并未生效",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "87e36a35-a52c-4413-9f30-5ca274734b4a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -15157.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "嵌套对象的解构",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7f102371-b667-47e0-9cd0-232b36ede41b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -15157.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "let obj = {\n    p: [\n\n        'Hello',\n\n        {y: 'World'}\n\n    ]\n\n};\n\nlet {p: [x, {y: name}]} = obj;\n\nconsole.log(x); // Hello\n\nconsole.log(name); // World\n\nconsole.log(y); // ReferenceError: y is not deﬁned",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5afd1313-5aab-4587-b982-c29981ed7e23",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -14997.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "选择性解构对象的属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "08134247-06b9-46e1-b46e-05c00377493c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -14997.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "let { min, max } = Math;\nconsole.log(min(1, 3));  // 1\n\nconsole.log(max(1, 3));  // 3",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "165ee9a1-225e-4bf5-87fe-ac6322204e1f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -14837.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "函数参数解构",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1ff702e2-458c-4e6f-9ea9-ae5e16303fde",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -14837.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "function whois({displayName: displayName, fullName: {ﬁrstName: name}}){\n    console.log(displayName + \"is\" + name);\n\n}\n\nconst user = {\n\n    id: 42,\n\n    displayName: \"jdoe\",\n\n    fullName: {\n\n        ﬁrstName: \"John\",\n\n        lastName: \"Doe\"\n\n    }\n\n};\n\nwhois(user); // jdoe is John",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0c814729-d64c-4914-a4a1-475707f90952",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1310.3662298828126,
      "y": -13667.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "扩展运算符与rest运算符",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "69d954ab-b7d2-464d-956a-313d728c52f4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -14467.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "扩展运算符",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ac11b753-77b8-4e59-96af-4a83a2ae2904",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -14677.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "定义",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a9e27184-2c14-4f4c-8f12-a071957cbf53",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -14677.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "扩展运算符用3个点表示（...），用于将一个数组或类数组对象转换为用逗号分隔的值序列",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "05ce25b6-e0f0-45cd-9e4f-6d0a5050b388",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -14677.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "const array = [1, 2, 3, 4];\nconsole.log(...array); // 1 2 3 4\n\nconst str = \"string\";\n\nconsole.log(...str); // s t r i n g",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d9b97184-44f7-4fe4-a52f-95f31ada861b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -14257.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "使用场景",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "23188c99-d9f7-45aa-b820-e499b87c8efc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -14517.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "扩展运算符代替apply()函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "43591abc-f3ca-452c-9ec5-e737a15d2868",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -14517.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "console.log(Math.max(...arr)); // 8",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "40ada642-ffc9-4f3f-91f1-f8a527757cc9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -14357.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "扩展运算符代替concat()函数合并数组",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e423d394-6819-4bfb-9a02-075adbe76c58",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -14357.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "console.log([...arr1, ...arr2]); // [ 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6 ]",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "fd03f92c-41bc-41fa-b949-a4567060ca1c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -14197.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "扩展运算符转换Set，得到去重的数组",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1c3ecbc6-f776-4269-807e-c6a4096412cb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -14197.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "let arr = [1, 2, 4, 6, 2, 7, 4];\nconsole.log([...new Set(arr)]); // [ 1, 2, 4, 6, 7 ]",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d14b75c4-f84a-4560-8f4f-b4217a76f0cb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -13957.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "扩展运算符用于对象克隆",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7838c67d-4690-4d4e-8c8a-3c89d8cca1ce",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -14037.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "let obj = {name: 'kingx'};\nvar obj2 = {...obj};\n\nobj2.name = 'kingx2';\n\nconsole.log(obj); // {name: \"kingx\"}",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f2a99471-8b34-4591-82a9-b22b05d91b4a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -13877.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "使用扩展运算符对数组或对象进行克隆时，如果数组的元素或者对象的属性是基本数据类型，则支持深克隆；如果是引用数据类型，则不支持深克隆",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "21f45e43-fc5d-437f-a6ce-44e85615b578",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -13537.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "rest运算符",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ac8b4ea6-2a15-4a6c-a934-10eefbc43f40",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -13717.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "定义",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8e9cfd2d-4213-4a8d-a40e-1e5001d3fe8c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -13717.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "rest运算符同样使用3个点表示（...），其作用与扩展运算符相反，用于将以逗号分隔的值序列转换成数组",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e0a19a5a-7f94-42ed-b781-2de26658e576",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -13357.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "使用场景",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "030c41a6-a048-4f4e-97cf-c2dab14b7bc3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -13477.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "rest运算符与解构组合使用",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d7563e86-fab8-445d-b88c-030574e1d44e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -13557.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "let arr = ['one', 'two', 'three', 'four'];\nlet [arg1, ...arg2] = arr;\n\nconsole.log(arg1);  // one\n\nconsole.log(arg2);  // [ 'two', 'three', 'four' ]",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f814960e-aaec-4a86-9caa-4dbec960bbe9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -13397.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "需要注意的是，如果想要使用rest运算符进行解构，则rest运算符对应的变量应该放在最后一位，否则就会抛出异常。因为如果rest运算符不是放在最后一位，变量并不知道要读取多少个数值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "cb1b3f2b-519a-4ce5-8a2e-a3b7ef4154f5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": -13397.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "let arr = ['one', 'two', 'three', 'four'];\nlet [...arg1, arg2] = arr; // SyntaxError: Rest element must be last element \n\nin array",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d86485b8-ff92-45af-885e-1c61ef84b616",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -13237.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "rest运算符代替arguments处理函数参数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "99910849-3b8e-4a81-9e10-0cd17fc9cf11",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -13237.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "function foo(...args) {\n    for (let arg of args) {\n\n        console.log(arg);\n\n    }\n\n}\n\nfoo('one', 'two', 'three', 'four');// 输出'one', 'two', 'three', 'four'",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e0766d95-3d7a-4517-9b25-1de184f84cfa",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -12997.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "区别",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1a0333a4-7134-4df2-a94e-374cc333ca66",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -13077.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "当3个点（…）出现在函数的形参上或者出现在赋值等号的左侧，则表示它为rest运算符",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "233d27d7-8c5d-4084-8096-a6c2aef9c6dc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -12917.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "当3个点（…）出现在函数的实参上或者出现在赋值等号的右侧，则表示它为扩展运算符",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "98536b59-9b34-4624-a83f-7cae963a06f5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1310.3662298828126,
      "y": -12757.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "模版字符串",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b836d6ff-13f1-4353-9bad-e2072ca255d0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -12757.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "模板字符串使用反引号（``）括起来，它可以当作普通的字符串使用，也可以用来定义多行字符串，同时支持在字符串中使用${}嵌入变量",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "be39a2c3-f65b-4950-b021-f54f7efe709b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1310.3662298828126,
      "y": -12157.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "箭头函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "08b3b85d-74b0-4259-941b-6eef840fa020",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -12437.12428589382,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "特点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8ac7e503-1872-4829-a222-10c55e2aac4b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -12597.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不绑定this",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1893ec88-0a74-45d2-8ff5-84ca16abcb19",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -12437.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不支持call和apply函数的特性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "09dfebf8-ec0c-4131-8a99-922d6aef610f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -12277.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不绑定arguments",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "09ee24b6-3fc6-496c-bde9-45e7bdae17e4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -12277.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "虽然无法通过arguments来获取实参，但是可以借助rest运算符（...）来达到这个目的",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "23947dc4-302f-48ff-8a85-ada0ed0c1a1a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -11877.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不适用场景",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d5e765ef-218d-43bc-9c1c-7be19ec796d8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -12117.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不适合作为对象的函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5a162db6-4c43-4a2c-955d-1a7ee71ce245",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -12117.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "this将会指向外层作用域，并不会指向对象本身",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "60f7ab16-909c-4971-897b-a67403576a78",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -11957.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不能作为构造函数，不能使用new操作符",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7a7c375e-55f1-4db9-bbc1-a474dc6f8bd3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -11957.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "构造函数是通过new操作符生成对象实例的，生成实例的过程也是通过构造函数给实例绑定this的过程，而箭头函数没有自己的this。因此不能使用箭头函数作为构造函数，也就不能通过new操作符来调用箭头函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a059ffc9-22dc-449e-85f5-dbfe0a3feb33",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -11797.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "没有prototype属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d4d55201-a982-4854-bf9e-ce6a8d3c2760",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -11797.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "因为在箭头函数中是没有this的，也就不存在自己的作用域，因此箭头函数是没有prototype属性的",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a7caa007-40fb-4611-a620-d8edbf82eea4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -11637.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不适合将原型函数定义成箭头函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3236d68e-3c50-4d0f-a4ce-d905ffd0ee75",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -11637.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在给构造函数添加原型函数时，如果使用箭头函数，其中的this会指向全局作用域window，而并不会指向构造函数，因此并不会访问到构造函数本身，也就无法访问到实例属性，这就失去了作为原型函数的意义",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b0ed08ab-2303-432e-ad2d-959286209a91",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1310.3662298828126,
      "y": -10890.457619227152,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d0fc7a87-1da3-4f5d-87a4-3a0f51ec6675",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -11477.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "属性简写",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "39be0f21-736b-48c6-86fa-126445542d5e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -10997.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "属性遍历",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1fad913b-95bc-4fb4-ad6f-e0e5e7753b31",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -11317.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "for...in",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5a0403e5-67aa-423c-8dbf-c51fb72e594d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -11317.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "对象自身和继承的可枚举属性（不包含Symbol属性）",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a9655e02-dbbc-454d-9535-7a667a09d794",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -11157.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Object.keys(obj)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e949d1d7-ad6d-4470-97ea-58e1fe027179",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -11157.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "对象自身所有可枚举属性，不包含继承属性和Symbol属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0f8dfef5-846d-4afe-a0fe-e09180fe725b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -10997.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Object.getOwnPropertyNames(obj)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "bfcaddae-934f-4358-a6ce-f42573e1f8af",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -10997.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "对象自身所有可枚举属性和不可枚举属性，不包含继承属性和Symbol属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6ae131b1-cfd4-4c39-a0c8-19400fe9dc34",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -10837.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Object.getOwnPropertySymbols(obj)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b7526db7-1446-411f-8222-477c99e5209b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -10837.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "对象自身所有Symbol属性，不包含其他属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3f18551c-8eb0-4bbe-8cb1-566d8a31b6dd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -10677.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Reflect.ownKeys(obj)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9faa92eb-aea6-494f-8871-34cd9c59edd3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -10677.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "可枚举属性、不可枚举属性以及Symbol属性，不包含继承属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b5c922f3-fbef-4f98-be03-fa426b973cda",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -10197.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Object.assign()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "06f14f82-e2c2-4c0d-a2a2-e3091b447bf8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -10437.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "用于将一个或者多个对象的可枚举属性赋值给目标对象，然后返回目标对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0b690e52-b900-42e4-bbdf-205d24612945",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -10517.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "无法复制对象的不可枚举属性和继承属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "485af672-ba38-470e-990b-6d92f75c325f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -10357.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "可以复制可枚举的Symbol属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "899b66f7-68fd-4390-95fa-48efc7e98508",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -9957.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "用法",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "881ef0a5-4080-4e0d-8d78-bc076a2ee5a5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -10197.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "对象克隆",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "828e3e31-4457-4523-b5e2-44e7e997cd1c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -10037.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "给对象添加属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "82b1f2fb-db15-4a38-989d-d1d420e0dea9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -9877.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "给对象添加函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "64c1e587-28aa-4830-9d59-82bf0c5e7255",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -9717.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "合并对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "352d8edb-1656-4bed-892f-e92c6d5f9b05",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1310.3662298828126,
      "y": -8967.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Symbol",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b37e5ea8-8ff9-4ce2-b7d5-96da317eeb74",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -9297.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "特性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "40fb4c92-95ac-43f3-a35e-00b9ecfb22cd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -9557.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "唯一性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e031869f-82e1-46cd-94b9-72cf94f3d86c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -9557.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "任何通过Symbol()函数创建的Symbol值都是不相同的，即使传递了相同的字符串",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "297fc4f6-ec43-4cfa-8fa2-9ea82cd1930e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -9397.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不能使用new操作符",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5129bd7c-9f53-455e-a9dd-c111782f4033",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -9397.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Symbol函数并不是一个构造函数，因此不能通过new操作符创建Symbol值。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f326993a-7fac-48e4-993b-ac7c720f0eab",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -9237.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不能参与类型运算",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "48d9bf89-dce8-4842-98fc-8017c3224d2e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -9237.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Symbol值可以通过toString()函数显示地转换为字符串，但是本身不能参与其他类型值的运算，例如在对Symbol值进行字符串拼接操作时，会抛出异常",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "699c4b34-4b03-4844-a86a-c7c2b0a599e2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -8997.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "可以使用同一个Symbol值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f23dfa47-ffd5-48e9-8296-00811807eec9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -9077.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "使用Symbol.for()函数，它接收一个字符串作为参数，然后搜索有没有以该参数作为名称的Symbol值。如果有，就返回这个Symbol值，否则就新建并返回一个以该字符串为名称的Symbol值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "823c77b6-11cd-4d6c-9cfd-e2a81b1b1c8b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -8917.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "let s1 = Symbol.for('one');\nlet s2 = Symbol.for('one');\n\ns1 === s2; // true",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "374f1ea6-37e0-4426-8aeb-7e2f3ebe6bb2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -8637.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "用法",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f3cb89e8-24ac-4a48-bd30-f54a4398fb06",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -8757.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "用作对象属性名",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "dbdfbd6a-d74c-46f1-b85e-8ca11a6aa224",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -8517.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "用于属性名遍历",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1e7e9c2e-cc5a-4d1e-a357-7011015504b3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -8597.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "使用Symbol作为属性名时，不能通过Object.keys()函数或者for...in来枚举，这样我们可以将一些不需要对外操作和访问的属性通过Symbol来定义",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "2edf04a1-2112-44af-b664-e7b6ce890f00",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -8437.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "因为Symbol属性不会出现在属性遍历的过程中，所以在使用JSON.stringify()函数将对象转换为JSON字符串时，Symbol值也不会出现在结果中",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "95fb967a-082d-4b09-a779-370515d966a7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1310.3662298828126,
      "y": -7369.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Set",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d2b9ed76-2a1d-459a-8fc2-01702cacb09d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -8277.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "定义",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "923c6c01-77cd-4b04-9ec1-e98c971b22ba",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -8277.124285893819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "表示的是一组数据的集合，成员值都是唯一的，没有重复",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "437b81e5-7343-4141-aca9-ef6a3a81514d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -8037.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6fc57a1d-11be-41b9-9972-a04000b92be2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -8117.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Set.prototype.constructor",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3d7e0c16-b104-4603-bb17-6630f337b3d6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -8117.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "构造函数，默认就是Set函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "871e3944-e661-4bb7-a51a-6141b49d3781",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -7957.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Set.prototype.size",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b2bbd605-2d7a-4085-adc9-285b568e6e5e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -7957.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "返回实例的成员总数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "76ccda9e-9bf9-48b0-b95f-38ce1e7689c9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -7417.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1ea21fe5-0752-45a1-9b99-fce3f589ff80",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -7717.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Set.prototype.add(value)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "181e3a68-ea37-4206-8652-9f3a78fd0a04",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -7717.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "添加一个值，返回Set结构本身",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9ccc0a7d-1c4c-4327-b408-6426c7574fb0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -7797.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "添加新的值时，不会发生类型转换。这可以理解为使用add()函数添加新值时，新值与Set实例中原有值是采用严格相等（===）进行比较的，只有在严格相等的比较结果为不相等时，才会将新值添加到Set实例中",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ef8c3f42-be85-4e01-b255-7bcdaa589367",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -7637.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "NaN与NaN在进行严格相等的比较时是不相等的，但是在Set内部，NaN与NaN是严格相等的，因此一个Set实例中只可以添加一个NaN",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e351bf51-9808-4370-81f6-d712c7b13aee",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -7477.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Set.prototype.delete(value)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a3cfb779-c725-4a41-b5ab-18c25a458276",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -7477.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "删除某个值，返回布尔值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f9902a3c-ff25-4b82-aee3-20be9d7fc80e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -7317.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Set.prototype.has(value)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f3ce2be0-6ad6-4a47-a6e2-7e98a7cc6e9a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -7317.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "返回布尔值，表示是否是成员",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "608bf96c-6192-4345-95cd-47881a18f383",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -7157.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Set.prototype.clear()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3e95f3f5-5239-4484-a074-732da6b5e410",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -7157.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "清除所有成员，无返回值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0e596655-ce61-4168-b503-ff590f0189fa",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -6837.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "用法",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a5759373-4ef7-4bfb-b2ce-c2aa4dc3ae95",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -6997.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "单一数组的去重",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4affb7b1-ac73-49f7-8069-7335f508bf6d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -6997.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "let arr = [1, 3, 4, 2, 3, 2, 5];\nconsole.log(new Set(arr)); // Set { 1, 3, 4, 2, 5 }",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "cef99b7b-5d78-41b6-90b7-d2e93cc7fe26",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -6837.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "多个数组的合并去重",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "49cd4c1a-0628-40bd-bb76-f8298304a72e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -6837.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "let arr1 = [1, 2, 3, 4];\nlet arr2 = [2, 3, 4, 5, 6];\n\nlet set1 = new Set([...arr1, ...arr2]);\n\nconsole.log(set1); // Set { 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6 }",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c1afe173-0ab8-4117-911a-a0a93733fd45",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -6677.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Set与数组的转换",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4efb28cd-acaf-4616-a352-0bf379219873",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -6677.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "let arr = [1, 3, 5, 7];\n// 将数组转换为Set\n\nlet set = new Set(arr);\n\nconsole.log(set);  // Set { 1, 3, 5, 7 }\n\nlet set = new Set();\n\nset.add('a');\n\nset.add('b');\n\n// 将Set转换为数组，通过Array.from()函数\n\nlet arr = Array.from(set);\n\nconsole.log(arr);  // [ 'a', 'b' ]\n\n// 将Set转换为数组，通过扩展运算符\n\nlet arr2 = [...set];\n\nconsole.log(arr2);  // [ 'a', 'b' ]",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4d217055-2f24-41eb-9e7b-dee414b49907",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -6277.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "遍历",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b5961592-fbb2-4c3f-a6ec-2775b75325fe",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -6517.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "forEach()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "fd8e6e99-dbff-4679-963d-6e1b91362f76",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -6517.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "第二个参数与第一个参数相同，也返回数据值本身",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3a0ee65c-aff9-45a7-8173-b225b9c65d38",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -6037.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "迭代器",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c6e0d7fd-740f-4537-ba60-bcef6e6115d6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -6357.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "keys()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e339624e-fa3c-484e-824c-8c9c2716d56d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -6357.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "返回键名的遍历器",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "35a7cadd-28cd-433e-bc3d-0e85cda00fcc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -6197.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "values()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a4aee8d6-3620-4e32-9ff1-102fcb7712b8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -6197.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "返回键值的遍历器",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1975c1a3-d78d-4beb-b981-0472db005e87",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -6037.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "entries()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ed7cda70-a900-4dd5-a741-e5406d05d0fe",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -6037.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "返回键值对的遍历器",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "331d62da-de26-4675-9b91-0688981a5c2d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -5877.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "因为Set实例的键和值是相等的，所以keys()函数和values()函数实际返回的是相同的值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "775405e2-14ab-4791-939a-6e3a7ab2cbb3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -5717.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "获得的对象都是遍历器对象Iterator，然后通过for...of循环可以获取每一项的值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d11f3f42-80b8-46d9-ad16-f615d6e21fba",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1310.3662298828126,
      "y": -4509.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Map",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7ef6beab-ae79-4240-82bd-1c9e814d2a40",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -5557.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "定义",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "405c1bac-9f8a-44f8-af85-7b08a0651173",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -5557.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "表示一种键值对的组合",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5a19d289-7224-4e22-973e-42aa6d1d2009",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -5557.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "与对象字面量不同的是，对象字面量的键只能是字符串，对于非字符串类型的值会采用强制类型转换成字符串，而Map的键却可以由各种类型的值组成",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a460060d-8b52-40a6-bc19-6e3f66c1af42",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -5397.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "87319dfd-e619-42a1-87bb-12e01fe66aa6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -5397.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "size",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b64536c9-1581-423a-91ad-e11078bbab1b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -5397.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "返回Map结构的成员总数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "dcc0ac53-b8f2-4e5d-916a-8a2a53545320",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -4917.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5e2bd30b-5f64-48bd-b3e7-3ad2caafe0d4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -5237.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "set(key, value)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a0bb1ca7-99e7-4a1c-8a99-dbc12d3fb91c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -5237.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "set()函数设置键名key对应的键值为value，set()函数返回的是当前Map对象，因此set()函数可以采用链式调用的写法",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "101f4db5-5e65-4572-9e40-a1f34618642e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -5237.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "+0和-0严格相等，虽然NaN与NaN不严格相等，但是Map会将其视为一个相同的键",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4540b3ae-6a32-4951-91e3-7f280c56ce5e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -5077.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "get(key)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9330aa49-481b-4d29-b4c0-251eb5c727bc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -5077.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "get()函数读取key对应的键值，如果找不到key，返回“undefined”",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "2fc8d25a-bdc6-4fe8-b3ba-f8a2baa3ab31",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -4917.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "has(key)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "73c5c6c0-f742-4036-89ac-4b58db9c25e4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -4917.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "has()函数返回一个布尔值，表示某个键是否在当前Map对象中",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "de3278b8-1ff6-461e-b9cc-619a6f47c99e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -4757.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "delete(key)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "847cbf43-2eb3-47ca-bb56-8bde64b54fb1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -4757.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "delete()函数删除某个键，返回“true”；如果删除失败，返回“false”",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f79bd68d-58ed-43eb-8872-2ea0d271f4f6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -4597.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "clear()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e71ea01c-542b-49d3-8488-d3e004abd324",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -4597.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "clear()函数清除所有成员，没有返回值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "045e0e7b-5e49-4415-aa49-e81f892f4749",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -4237.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "遍历",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6e398be9-01e7-4e16-83bf-e97fda830227",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -4437.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "forEach()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9643d2a5-c8b1-4eeb-bac3-208a83fd0a6b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -4437.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "第一个参数表示的是值，第二个参数表示的是键",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d3f492a5-c20e-4d2c-9e77-ca1ce88e8ac4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -4037.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "迭代器",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d2d90502-7c2f-4416-9d0f-de277d7e7868",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -4277.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "keys()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a83db7ea-83eb-41c7-a881-482cf6ccc922",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -4277.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "返回键名的遍历器",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4e56fd36-230a-406e-af30-b9ae2228f2c2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -4117.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "values()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a561f5b6-d78c-41e9-9f35-ab461e796f8c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -4117.1242858938185,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "返回键值的遍历器",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "894ee8a3-dac4-43ba-b881-e5f1d6834bdd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -3957.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "entries()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1f0813b1-b71d-4fbb-b389-1064d2a942e5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -3957.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "返回键值对的遍历器",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "30fe6c02-bcc5-4af4-bc73-e90c8c25a40d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -3797.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "获得的对象都是遍历器对象Iterator，然后通过for...of循环可以获取每一项的值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4e7677f3-5f75-4bd8-82b2-9085476ddf03",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -2437.1242858938162,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "数据转换",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "45cb3b86-06d6-40f4-bf10-ee68a911bfe2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -3557.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Map转换为数组",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a6bebc0d-01c8-48cb-9047-0166612d0ff9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -3637.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "通过扩展运算符实现",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "2d731229-082d-4c1c-84d6-69bdbbc507a4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -3477.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "//Map转换为数组\nconst map = new Map();\n\nmap.set('name', 'kingx');\n\nmap.set('age', 12);\n\nconst arr = [...map];\n\nconsole.log(arr); // [ [ 'name', 'kingx' ], [ 'age', 12 ] ]",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d7199dfd-5239-423c-847d-abc440807eb9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -3237.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "数组转换为Map",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "2cc1bbeb-715f-4bc1-aabc-4fc6dfcd62a5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -3317.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "通过Map构造函数实现，使用new操作符生成Map的实例",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a75a6b7c-5902-4c3e-8914-7a703061d5af",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -3157.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "//Map转换为对象\nconst arr = [[ 'name', 'kingx' ], [ 'age', 12 ]];\n\nconst map = new Map(arr);\n\nconsole.log(map);  // Map { 'name' => 'kingx', 'age' => 12 }",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "191679e1-ecc1-45ff-8aef-07b604ab18bf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -2917.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Map转换为对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "18fbc71c-a2ef-4584-b68e-345fea9d2836",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -2997.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果Map的实例的键是字符串，则可以直接转换；如果键不是字符串，则会先转换成字符串然后再进行转换",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d36a4c89-b07c-4022-b573-afd5b895e3ba",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -2837.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "// Map转换为对象\nfunction mapToObj(map) {\n\n    let obj = {};\n\n    for(let [key, value] of map) {\n\n        obj[key] = value;\n\n    }\n\n    return obj;\n\n}\n\nconsole.log(mapToObj(map));  // { name: 'kingx', age: 12 }",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c318194b-a137-4400-b008-54e420a24473",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -2597.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "对象转换为Map",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "89bf189f-8fb9-46de-9151-a7fbeeaa369e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -2677.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "遍历对象的属性并通过set()函数添加到Map的实例中",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b700c0a7-485b-49bb-b15a-fc0bfbb026d4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -2517.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "// 对象转换为Map\nfunction objToMap(obj) {\n\n    let map = new Map();\n\n    for (let k of Object.keys(obj)) {\n\n        map.set(k, obj[k]);\n\n    }\n\n    return map;\n\n}\n\nconsole.log(objToMap({yes: true, no: false}));\n\n// Map {\"yes\" => true, \"no\" => false}",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1235b8b0-38c0-4e67-97fe-25611a218c1e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -2277.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Map转换为JSON字符串",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6343e315-fcff-4371-9260-93ab01302d6a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -2357.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "当Map的键名都是字符串时，可以先将Map转换为对象，然后调用JSON.stringify()函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "641eead3-2ad4-4638-b213-d9d918a5121b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -2357.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "// Map转换为JSON，通过对象\nfunction mapToJson(strMap) {\n\n    // 先将map转换为对象，然后转换为JSON\n\n    return JSON.stringify(mapToObj(strMap));\n\n}\n\nlet myMap = new Map().set('yes', true).set('no', false);\n\nconsole.log(mapToJson(myMap)); // {\"yes\":true,\"no\":false}",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "866c616e-3682-46b6-9d5f-a3c68442eeb6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -2197.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "当Map的键名有非字符串时，我们可以先将Map转换为数组，然后调用JSON.stringify()函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e5be2036-1503-4fc4-9f07-3e174be14e80",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -2197.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "// Map转换为JSON,通过数组\nfunction mapToArrayJson(map) {\n\n    // 先通过扩展运算符转换为数组，再转换为JSON\n\n    return JSON.stringify([...map]);\n\n}\n\nlet myMap2 = new Map().set(true, 7).set({foo: 3}, ['abc']);\n\nmapToArrayJson(myMap2); // [[true,7],[{\"foo\":3},[\"abc\"]]]",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9080c6ec-5dbb-4528-abae-259320dab55b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -1957.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "JSON转换为Map",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e4657e62-e559-41d5-be3b-002fd5dc23c7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -2037.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "JSON字符串是由一系列键值对构成，键一般都为字符串。我们可以直接通过调用JSON.parse()函数先将JSON字符串转换为对象，然后再转换为Map",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "51c35a9f-7623-4161-a96d-844c5762c471",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -1877.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "// JSON转换为Map\nfunction jsonToMap(jsonStr) {\n\n    // 先转换为JSON对象，再转换为Map\n\n    return objToMap(JSON.parse(jsonStr));\n\n}\n\njsonToMap('{\"yes\": true, \"no\": false}'); // Map { 'yes' => true, 'no' => false }",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "03b98938-12f8-4d3c-aba7-59adb6d49945",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -1637.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Set转换为Map",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "505c9e75-2600-4e7d-b441-c60317b6a83e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -1717.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Set中以数组形式存在的数据可以直接通过Map的构造函数转换为Map",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "114b4c49-0c18-4aa2-b462-c2e6b1a8c9ef",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -1557.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "// Set转换为Map\nfunction setToMap(set) {\n\n    return new Map(set);\n\n}\n\nconst set = new Set([\n\n    ['foo', 1],\n\n    ['bar', 2]\n\n]);\n\nconsole.log(setToMap(set)); // Map { 'foo' => 1, 'bar' => 2 }",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8347c8c0-4be2-47b8-b8e9-17a225a2ba5b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -1317.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Map转换为Set",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0e06bc8a-51b7-4baf-a6c3-3832befe1287",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -1397.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "可以将遍历Map本身获取到的键和值构成一个数组，然后通过add()函数添加至set实例中",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6977d344-6953-4f88-abf2-36fe4a73d27d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -1237.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "// Map实例转换为Set\nfunction mapToSet(map) {\n\n    let set = new Set();\n\n    for (let [k,v] of map) {\n\n        set.add([k, v])\n\n    }\n\n    return set;\n\n}\n\nconst map14 = new Map()\n\n    .set('yes', true)\n\n    .set('no', false);\n\nmapToSet(map14); // Set { [ 'yes', true ], [ 'no', false ] }",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a2b8f7cf-14dd-4b02-882a-0c57fd9f396f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1310.3662298828126,
      "y": 1962.3628935933614,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Proxy",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "899039b2-1f6b-4f63-b7d7-f0a6fadf2a13",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -837.1242858938181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "定义",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7c3140d9-0c7c-4a86-8645-9da6460ed8f1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -997.1242858938181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "语法",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5a204e9a-8f5d-4637-ac04-b3d374c9caae",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -1077.124285893818,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "const proxy = new Proxy(target, handler)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f975536a-4091-471e-8825-68d38679014f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -917.1242858938181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "通过Proxy构造函数可以生成实例proxy，任何对proxy实例的属性的访问都会自动转发至target对象上，我们可以针对访问的行为配置自定义的handler对象，因此外界通过proxy访问target对象的属性时，都会执行handler对象自定义的拦截操作",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8277b9ff-02bc-444d-9e08-7d8aa15f6334",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -677.1242858938181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "注意点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "58eff0df-e453-454b-b51e-8e67449b96e1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -757.1242858938181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "必须通过代理实例访问",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ff22833a-270b-4341-8477-8beab4dadfe3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -757.1242858938181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果需要配置对象的拦截行为生效，那么必须是对代理实例的属性进行访问，而不是直接对目标对象进行访问",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "dd79f93c-c593-4097-998c-6197634cd503",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -597.1242858938181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "配置对象不能为空对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8e1d916d-fa21-4c6b-a982-d9f71f65f606",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -597.1242858938181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果需要配置对象的拦截行为生效，那么配置对象不能为空对象。如果为空对象，则代表没有设置任何拦截，实际是对目标对象的访问。另外配置对象不能为null，否则会抛出异常",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "bd2ef999-b59f-4baa-9617-2e0051800d05",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 1908.003919234387,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "实例函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f1317e22-c054-4ed8-bf9a-3319747b9cd1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 818.2603294907976,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "2ffbb29f-2668-4308-bdb6-410f4e3fa575",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -357.12428589381807,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "get(target, propKey, receiver)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c579c1c6-1d31-4729-a6fd-348f0d8746ed",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -437.12428589381807,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "拦截对象属性的读取操作",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3969961f-0f43-4b25-a6a4-e5b6e67259f2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -277.12428589381807,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "其中target表示的是目标对象，propKey表示的是读取的属性值，receiver表示的是配置对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7a80d6df-5768-4b3e-888f-d043e8e28814",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -37.12428589381807,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "set(target, propKey, value, receiver)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "02197a76-2866-4d35-97e4-785cc28ff077",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -117.12428589381807,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "拦截对象属性的写操作，即设置属性值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "52eb6839-56f4-4f76-8053-5fc88a721fd6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 42.87571410618193,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "其中target表示目标对象，propKey表示的是将要设置的属性，value表示将要设置的属性的值，receiver表示的是配置对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "417e5b5a-2570-460b-a275-5832084e840d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 202.87571410618193,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "has(target, propKey)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a7e0ee63-545f-4643-bdda-23f6d4281b40",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 202.87571410618193,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "拦截hasProperty的操作，返回一个布尔值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4ed4582c-9dff-4484-a5ee-698d60ca2a54",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 362.87571410618193,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "deleteProperty(target, propKey)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a6688f7a-a17f-4ab6-bd59-888a98249c78",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 362.87571410618193,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "拦截delete proxy[propKey]的操作，返回一个布尔值，表示是否执行成功",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "cfe7ca2c-1581-4cc7-ab90-97b8ff4d5baf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 522.8757141061819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "ownKeys(target)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f8da6517-a114-45a9-b8bb-55c711216fef",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 522.8757141061819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "拦截Object.getOwnPropertyNames(proxy)、Object.getOwnPropertySymbols(proxy)、Object.keys(proxy)、for...in循环等操作",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "02a630f9-bb45-4c3e-8f5f-7a87709a2fce",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 682.8757141061819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "getOwnPropertyDescriptor(target, propKey)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "de5880a6-257e-4c24-ab0a-46bb0b532956",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 682.8757141061819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "拦截Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptor(proxy, propKey)操作，返回属性的属性描述符构成的对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7504ad97-864f-4755-a231-896f155bcd45",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 842.8757141061819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "defineProperty(target, propKey, propDesc)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "21f2c0ae-18f0-465f-9fba-a5624e09e163",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 842.8757141061819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "拦截Object.defineProperty(proxy, propKey, propDesc）、Object.defineProperties(proxy,propDescs)操作，返回一个布尔值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "359042ac-0bcc-4f30-a1a9-6eaf2216736f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 1002.8757141061819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "preventExtensions(target)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0616b069-6b87-4f45-947f-86cfcd36d09f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 1002.8757141061819,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "拦截Object.preventExtensions(proxy)操作，返回一个布尔值，表示的是让一个对象变得不可扩展，不能再增加新的属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9dff130d-b138-41f8-b552-78eac71edf54",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 1162.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "getPrototypeOf(target)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "88b47191-eebe-493a-8752-a61a6393b5b2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 1162.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "拦截Object.getPrototypeOf(proxy)操作，返回一个对象，表示的是拦截获取对象原型属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "09747bce-fb56-4acd-932a-2699ef6e7e11",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 1322.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "isExtensible(target)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7993a1c5-4308-4963-867f-fb3a6f82f50b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 1322.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "拦截Object.isExtensible(proxy)，返回一个布尔值，表示对象是否是可扩展的",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "227c29ec-ac86-47a0-963a-3bea018aa12d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 1482.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "setPrototypeOf(target, proto)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "751ca084-7d94-4c52-925d-0a0b273314a2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 1482.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "拦截Object.setPrototypeOf(proxy, proto)操作，返回一个布尔值，表示的是拦截设置对象的原型属性的行为",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e2ef7123-66b3-459d-b24e-d2c40c78636e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 1642.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "apply(target, object, args)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6b3ab3bf-3b8d-43c3-b9af-58dd97e259b1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 1642.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "拦截Proxy实例作为函数调用的操作，例如proxy(...args)、proxy.call(object,...args)、proxy.apply(...)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "78509c03-b48d-40d6-8a90-511e1454bfaf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 1802.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "construct(target, args)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8d871107-43dc-4e2c-93ed-4bef92bba512",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 1802.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "拦截Proxy实例作为构造函数调用的操作，例如new proxy(...args)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "355944f9-a188-4d9a-b347-23e34c0f4536",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 1962.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "注意",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "eb746062-7012-48ab-b08e-1d402558e9bb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 1962.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "这些函数都有一个通用的特性，即如果在target中使用了this关键字，再通过Proxy处理后，this关键字指向的是Proxy的实例，而不是目标对象target",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d9deb469-d1b8-409c-8655-fe13979272d5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 2942.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "应用场景",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c0594aa9-6f31-4899-af15-69945879889a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 2122.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "读取不存在属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "28615e84-78fc-4971-9699-6671d42aec7c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 2122.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在正常情况下，读取一个对象不存在的属性时，会返回“undefined”。通过Proxy的get()函数可以设置读取不存在的属性时抛出异常，从而避免对undefined值的兼容性处理",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "bbd78278-0d6a-4b55-bd54-6da91a203543",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 2122.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "let person = {\n    name: 'kingx'\n\n};\n\nconst proxy = new Proxy(person, {\n\n    get: function (target, propKey) {\n\n        if(propKey in target) {\n\n            return target[propKey];\n\n        } else {\n\n            throw new ReferenceError(`访问的属性${propKey}不存在`);\n\n        }\n\n    }\n\n});\n\nconsole.log(proxy.name); // kingx\n\nconsole.log(proxy.age); // ReferenceError: 访问的属性age不存在",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "23ab2010-6805-40bb-837b-9fd4902764b4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 2362.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "读取负索引的值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5e4ef883-7e2b-4437-9f69-3c9e3c7e0192",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 2362.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "数组的索引值是从0开始依次递增的，正常情况下我们无法读取负索引的值，但是通过Proxy的get()函数可以做到这一点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "85cd93d1-ad13-4252-89a8-457171e1400a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 2282.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "负索引实际就是从数组的尾部元素开始，从后往前，寻找元素的位置",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "103d4281-d6dc-43fb-9080-fb35be33fa57",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 2442.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "const arr = [1, 4, 9, 16, 25];\nconst proxy = new Proxy(arr, {\n\n    get: function (target, index) {\n\n        index = Number(index);\n\n        if (index > 0) {\n\n            return target[index];\n\n        } else {\n\n            // 索引为负值，则从尾部元素开始计算索引\n\n            return target[target.length + index];\n\n        }\n\n    }\n\n});\n\nconsole.log(proxy[2]);  // 9\n\nconsole.log(proxy[-2]); // 16",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "fb50d7e5-21f8-461e-b5f2-3515b480f1da",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 2602.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "禁止访问私有属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5c31b7fa-4ee5-4fc0-bc9b-4f1f3706d733",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 2602.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在一些约定俗成的写法中，私有属性都会以下画线（_）开头，事实上我们并不希望用户能访问到私有属性，这可以通过设置Proxy的get()函数来实现",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "42e1d475-c2f4-4fb7-907b-af292cc6fed7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 2602.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "const person = {\n    name: 'kingx',\n\n    _pwd: '123456'\n\n};\n\nconst proxy = new Proxy(person, {\n\n    get: function (target, prop) {\n\n        if (prop.indexOf('_') === 0) {\n\n            throw new ReferenceError('不可直接访问私有属性');\n\n        } else {\n\n            return target[prop];\n\n        }\n\n    }\n\n});\n\nconsole.log(proxy.name); // kingx\n\nconsole.log(proxy._pwd); // ReferenceError: 不可直接访问私有属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f8e4ce7b-acce-4d5a-9678-27482df22c7c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 2762.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Proxy访问属性的限制",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a904b8fc-df44-48e0-9563-385db1dcc9b7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 2762.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "我们期望使用Proxy对对象的属性进行代理，并修改属性的返回值时，我们需要这个属性不能同时为不可配置和不可写。如果这个属性同时为不可配置和不可写，那么在通过代理读取属性时，会抛出异常。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f80894f5-1019-4892-a1dd-4fbe97479471",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 2762.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不可写且不可配置的属性只能返回其实际值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "04d866e3-6f7a-42c9-af4d-04d63c14005d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 2922.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "拦截属性赋值操作",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "31478b6e-b37c-4100-a454-d6b16e4516bd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 2922.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "set()函数会拦截属性的赋值操作",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4970481f-c7ca-4557-a698-170898815bb8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 2922.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "const proxy = new Proxy({}, {\n    set: function (target, prop, value) {\n\n        if (prop === 'age') {\n\n            if (!Number.isInteger(value)) {\n\n                throw new TypeError('The age is not an integer');\n\n            }\n\n            if (value > 200 || value < 0) {\n\n                throw new RangeError('The age is invalid');\n\n            }\n\n        }  else {\n\n            target[prop] = value;\n\n        }\n\n    }\n\n});\n\nproxy.name = 'kingx';  // 正常\n\nproxy.age = 10;  // 正常\n\nproxy.age = 201; // RangeError: The age is invalid",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "17ad587a-df1c-4eb5-8c21-b7d1abe7781d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 3242.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "隐藏内部私有属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "12f7f07e-9172-481b-8a53-ba71cd321872",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 3082.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Proxy提供了has()函数，用于拦截hasProperty()函数，即判断对象是否具有某个属性，如果具有则返回“true”，如果不具有则返回“false”，典型的就是in操作符",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3aba8861-5d8e-4e76-a8f1-62fac6cf86fb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 3082.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "has()函数只会对in操作符生效，而不会对for...in循环操作符生效",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "982192fd-f7a8-4410-af07-b8fc84609e48",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 3242.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "需要注意的是has()函数判断的是hasProperty()函数，而不是hasOwnProperty()函数，即has()函数不判断一个属性是对象自身的属性，还是对象继承的属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "10da06a2-43f5-4ef3-ac86-403ca6b03a1c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 3402.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "has()函数有一个最大的用处就是隐藏某些以下画线开头（_）的私有属性，不对外暴露它们，从而通过in循环时不会遍历出私有属性值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a2026f5d-185a-4674-a5ac-96f18aface4e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 3402.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "const obj = {\n    _name: 'kingx',\n\n    age: 13\n\n};\n\nconst proxy = new Proxy(obj, {\n\n    has: function (target, prop) {\n\n        if(prop[0] === '_') {\n\n           return false;\n\n        }\n\n        return prop in target;\n\n    }\n\n});\n\nconsole.log('age' in proxy);   // true\n\nconsole.log('_name' in proxy); // false",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "65ed9cb7-a4d8-486e-8f34-f29c9f4a4e11",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 3642.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "禁止删除某些属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d6445fbc-b1b1-4c12-9a5f-fbb04c4a5e8c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 3562.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Proxy中提供了deleteProperty()函数，用于拦截delete操作，返回“true”时表示属性删除成功，返回“false”时表示属性删除失败",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3f1415a2-494b-4877-8573-b3c1cea8225b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 3722.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "利用这个特性，我们可以做特殊处理，不能删除以下画线开头的私有属性。当删除了私有属性时，会抛出异常，终止操作",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0b0e157c-64d5-43a3-9de9-285fb9378407",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 3722.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "let obj = {\n    _name: 'kingx',\n\n    age: 12\n\n};\n\nconst proxy = new Proxy(obj, {\n\n    deleteProperty: function (target, prop) {\n\n        if (prop[0] === '_') {\n\n            throw new Error(`Invalid attempt to delete private \"${prop}\" property`);\n\n        }\n\n        return true;\n\n    }\n\n});\n\ndelete proxy.age;  // 删除成功\n\ndelete proxy._name; // Error: Invalid attempt to delete private \"_name\" property",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6e4e828a-2ba6-4d7a-85c2-c22080348285",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 3882.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "函数的拦截",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b05cccd7-ce4f-4b89-9f82-d559fe1a98c1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 3882.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Proxy中提供了apply()函数，用于拦截函数调用的操作，函数调用包括直接调用、call()函数调用、apply()函数调用3种方式",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4099ac8b-700f-41fc-aa37-b0c055eef785",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 3882.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "function sum(num1, num2) {\n    return num1 + num2;\n\n}\n\nconst proxy = new Proxy(sum, {\n\n    apply: function (target, obj, args) {\n\n        return target.apply(obj, args) * 2;\n\n    }\n\n});\n\nconsole.log(proxy(1, 3));  // 8\n\nconsole.log(proxy.call(null, 3, 4));  // 14\n\nconsole.log(proxy.apply(null, [5, 6]));  // 22",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ffe2f8d9-60f3-4b04-805e-9247d3aa5046",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 4816.209047439515,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "使用场景",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "510a182b-beda-4c8e-b0d3-e0f57b87f901",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 4362.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "实现真正的私有",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "da70cc05-2ac4-453b-a7c0-20c20b8dc4f8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 4202.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "私有需要达到的目标",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "447cfd78-10ba-4503-92bd-be6bd61d88f8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 4042.875714106182,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不能访问到私有属性，如果访问到私有属性则返回“undefined”",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d2d0433a-6f7a-4529-800e-1fcec090ec98",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 4202.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不能直接修改私有属性的值，即使设置了也无效",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "25b6bde8-284a-4499-916a-93a1fcc95c84",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 4362.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不能遍历出私有属性，遍历出来的属性中不会包含私有属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b75ba715-5d4b-45f9-b668-e711ffdce1a3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 4522.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "const apis = {\n    _apiKey: '12ab34cd56ef',\n\n    getAllUsers: function () {\n\n        console.log('这是查询全部用户的函数');\n\n    },\n\n    getUserById: function (userId) {\n\n        console.log('这是根据用户id查询用户的函数');\n\n    },\n\n    saveUser: function (user) {\n\n        console.log('这是保存用户的函数');\n\n    }\n\n};\n\nconst proxy = new Proxy(apis, {\n\n    get: function (target, prop) {\n\n        if (prop[0] === '_') {\n\n            return undeﬁned;\n\n        }\n\n        return target[prop];\n\n    },\n\n    set: function (target, prop, value) {\n\n        if (prop[0] !== '_') {\n\n            target[prop] = value;\n\n        }\n\n    },\n\n    has: function (target, prop) {\n\n        if (prop[0] === '_') {\n\n            return false;\n\n        }\n\n        return prop in target;\n\n    }\n\n});\n\nconsole.log(proxy._apiKey); // undeﬁned\n\nconsole.log(proxy.getAllUsers()); // 这是查询全部用户的函数\n\nproxy._apiKey = '123456789'; // 设置无效\n\nconsole.log('getUserById' in proxy);  // true\n\nconsole.log('_apiKey' in proxy); // false",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "24c25b6a-3b1d-4fd1-bb96-5ea576bb9ffc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 4762.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "增加日志记录",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e56edeea-218a-4ff2-83ad-2bc344f690c1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 4682.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Proxy进行拦截，首先通过get()函数拦截到调用的函数名，然后通过apply()函数进行函数的调用",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d95e8c33-b6b9-4bf2-80c6-f3506c7d9991",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 4842.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "const apis = {\n    _apiKey: '12ab34cd56ef',\n\n    getAllUsers: function () {\n\n        console.log('这是查询全部用户的函数');\n\n    },\n\n    getUserById: function (userId) {\n\n        console.log('这是根据用户id查询用户的函数');\n\n    },\n\n    saveUser: function (user) {\n\n        console.log('这是保存用户的函数');\n\n    }\n\n};\n\n// 记录日志的方法\n\nfunction recordLog() {\n\n    console.log('这是记录日志的函数');\n\n}\n\nconst proxy = new Proxy(apis, {\n\n    get: function (target, prop) {\n\n        const value = target[prop];\n\n        return function (...args) {\n\n            // 此处调用记录日志的函数\n\n            recordLog();\n\n            // 调用真实的函数\n\n            return value.apply(null, args);\n\n        }\n\n    }\n\n});\n\nproxy.getAllUsers();",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "2038a978-5113-4502-a5d1-4dfd2b6212e0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 5322.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "提供友好提示或者阻止特定操作",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "169b241f-dabd-4763-8517-8b1396317008",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 5162.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "增加某些操作的友好提示或者阻止特定的操作，主要包括以下几类",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "fc74cf60-ea01-4da5-b4a2-de331442d047",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 5002.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "某些被弃用的函数被调用时，给用户提供友好提示",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6845087f-ec20-4983-bf05-4ebff162aadd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 5162.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "阻止删除属性的操作",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6f790297-f5cb-42eb-8142-21a56c434a31",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 5322.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "阻止修改某些特定的属性的操作",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ab9f3495-452d-4530-8fed-16ced4ae7a15",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 5482.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "let dataStore = {\n    noDelete: 1234,\n\n    oldMethod: function () {/*...*/},\n\n    doNotChange: “tried and true”\n\n};\n\nlet NO_DELETE = ['noDelete'];\n\nlet DEPRECATED = ['oldMethod'];\n\nlet NO_CHANGE = ['doNotChange'];\n\nconst proxy = new Proxy(dataStore, {\n\n    set(target, key, value, proxy) {\n\n        if (NO_CHANGE.includes(key)) {\n\n            throw Error(`Error! ${key} is immutable.`);\n\n        }\n\n        return true;\n\n    },\n\n    deleteProperty(target, key) {\n\n        if (NO_DELETE.includes(key)) {\n\n            throw Error(`Error! ${key} cannot be deleted.`);\n\n        }\n\n        return true;\n\n    },\n\n    get(target, key, proxy) {\n\n        if (DEPRECATED.includes(key)) {\n\n            console.warn(`Warning! ${key} is deprecated.`);\n\n        }\n\n        const val = target[key];\n\n        return typeof val === 'function' ?\n\n            function (...args) {\n\n                val.apply(null, args);\n\n            } : val;\n\n    }\n\n});\n\nproxy.doNotChange = \"foo\"; // Error! doNotChange is immutable.\n\ndelete proxy.noDelete; // Error! noDelete cannot be deleted.\n\nproxy.oldMethod(); // Warning! oldMethod is deprecated.",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a86e1278-b152-492b-9d41-6a336474f6ec",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1310.3662298828126,
      "y": 9969.097936328404,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Reflect",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4fd91c72-5ab7-49e3-b275-da92618ab4e1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 5914.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "定义",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d6552c2c-64e8-477d-8d26-6148793b92b6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 5642.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "什么是Reflect对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b8f0bc41-81d7-4e96-a997-a0403819d462",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 5642.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "有一个名为Reflect的全局对象，上面挂载了对象的某些特殊函数，这些函数可以通过类似于Reflect.apply()这种形式来调用，所有在Reflect对象上的函数要么可以在Object原型链中找到，要么可以通过命令式操作符实现",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5f46d41c-5ada-476c-ba26-5c655e237349",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 6186.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "为什么要新增Reflect对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "889cf280-8210-451b-8466-d6b7aab18ed8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 5802.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "更合理地规划与Object对象相关的API",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1c83d865-89ca-40a6-afde-5fd8ee10ab05",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 5802.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在ES6中，Object对象的一些明显属于语言内部的函数都会添加到Reflect对象中，这样Object对象与Reflect对象中会存在相同的处理函数。而在未来的设计中，语言内部的函数将只会添加到Reflect对象中",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "262c47ba-97a0-4793-918a-1e23cd9ae9a7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 5962.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "用一个单一的全局对象去存储这些函数，能够保持其他的JavaScript代码的整洁、干净。不然的话，这些函数可能是全局的，或者要通过原型来调用，不方便统一管理",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "2828390b-c55a-43d7-a0a9-38416783ae89",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 6122.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "将一些命令式的操作符如delete、in等使用函数来替代，这样做的目的是为了让代码更好维护，更容易向下兼容，同时也避免出现更多的保留字",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "41d3e386-df74-463c-afa0-c57523e79df0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 6362.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "修改Object对象的某些函数的返回结果，可以让其变得更合理，使得代码更好维护",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ed62d020-2672-4b73-b05b-aa51b76fd346",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 6282.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果一个对象obj是不能扩展的，那么在调用Object.defineProperty(obj, name, desc)时，会抛出一个异常。因此在传统的写法中，我们需要通过try...catch处理",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "282f2932-b83f-4c4f-af76-f2d30d34de4e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 6442.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "而使用Reflect.defineProperty(obj, name, desc)时，返回的是“false”，新的写法就可以通过if...else实现",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "2a762ac9-f5f6-4708-afa9-b224cecb79a6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 6682.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Reflect对象的函数与Proxy对象的函数一一对应，只要是Proxy对象的函数，就能在Reflect对象上找到对应的函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "52407b0e-5cc6-4d27-a6ae-fe95e7ebf626",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 6602.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "这就让Proxy对象可以方便地调用对应的Reflect对象上的函数，完成默认行为，并以此作为修改行为的基础",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ed9782c4-993c-4f9e-b581-8a08e340c8a4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 6762.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不管Proxy对象怎么修改默认行为，总可以在Reflect对象上获取默认行为",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3eb7686c-761b-45f3-840c-cc181eaa77a4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 10189.54238077285,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "静态函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "eb79d6bb-7def-4772-9511-4a1a3006762f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 6922.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "与Proxy对象不同的是，Reflect对象本身并不是一个构造函数，而是直接提供静态函数以供调用",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ab435a65-4b57-44a8-9e83-59bc6c1347f1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 10122.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Reflect对象的静态函数一共有13个",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d96d70f5-b862-4177-8b81-dfdf5c27af3c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 7242.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Reflect.apply(target, thisArg, args)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c917553f-dbea-468b-bbd0-ae44ef43341b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 7082.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "作用是通过指定的参数列表执行target函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "01c73053-fd9e-4920-8ea8-d7cf3e392e56",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 7242.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "等同于执行Function.prototype.apply.call(target, thisArg, args)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "150921e9-3476-4a7f-bbd3-806a30fa8c31",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 7402.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "其中target表示的是目标函数，thisArg表示的是执行target函数时的this对象，args表示的是参数列表",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "bf01e111-34db-40c2-8c14-ac2d3801d749",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 7722.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Reflect.construct(target, args [, newTarget])",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7a7f167e-98c5-4a59-8f85-516b0ccfe895",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 7562.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "作用是执行构造函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7e2a8426-63f2-4d36-9245-8a635a309e59",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 7722.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "等同于执行new target(...args)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "dce4401d-159c-4938-b920-1c89e76cbebb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 7882.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "其中target表示的是构造函数，args表示的是参数列表。newTarget是选填的参数，如果增加了该参数，则表示将newTarget作为新的构造函数；如果没有增加该参数，则仍然使用第一个参数target作为构造函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "95301400-afa8-4fb2-83b3-45cf65d66c53",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 8202.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Reflect.defineProperty(target, propKey, attributes)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6a116e2f-3151-4105-9b7f-9fad3d094f44",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 8042.8757141061815,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "作用是为对象定义属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "fa340a47-077d-420c-a876-5b9e29d2fb72",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 8202.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "等同于执行Object.defineProperty()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7db42883-d328-4a8a-ab7f-a4f181c827b3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 8362.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "其中target表示的是定义属性的目标对象，propKey表示的是新增的属性名，attributes表示的是属性描述符对象集",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "870e76d7-8f29-4233-a0f5-307ed9baff01",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 8682.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Reflect.deleteProperty(target, propKey)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a06a0b3f-4d3e-43de-946f-90938b20cc9a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 8522.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "作用是删除对象的属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "cd8d4755-a4c7-4ef3-aa3c-17a25d870b20",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 8682.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "等同于执行deleteobj[propKey]",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "36b0b07a-10c2-42f8-8095-249c515ed4c8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 8842.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "其中target表示的是待删除属性的对象，propKey表示的是待删除的属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7c4c5c5d-1e3a-47dd-8f35-6b346a8ae424",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 9162.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Reflect.get(target, propKey, receiver)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e220efe7-4633-4c0b-b896-8e900d0eaf34",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 9002.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "作用是获取对象的属性值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "659aea1d-3cd6-46ed-a261-aa8f1a1e99c3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 9162.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "等同于执行target[propKey]",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d53ac429-966d-4117-8c5a-bc7be4d04317",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 9322.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "其中target表示的是获取属性的对象，propKey表示的是获取的属性，receiver表示函数中this绑定的对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1724b8d5-d3c8-4f8f-bc7b-a7f4fc243697",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 9642.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Reflect.getOwnPropertyDescriptor(target, propKey)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c82a35ea-b216-461e-b9c0-19474f2fd6bc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 9482.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "作用是得到指定属性的描述对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9e10c3f6-2bf3-4d4e-a823-d5d207f32176",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 9642.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "等同于执行Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptor()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "683a5df2-c881-49b3-8581-74da9bba3738",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 9802.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "其中target表示的是待操作的对象，propKey表示的是指定的属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b66f9a6a-cc8c-4dff-8b57-0a30ae1b13fe",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 10122.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Reflect.getPrototypeOf(target)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "cdecd7b8-01ad-4ca5-88c2-9f4c24bf1c75",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 9962.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "作用是读取对象的__proto__属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1f9e18ad-b7d8-4b57-8c7e-3977a6884298",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 10122.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "等同于执行Object.getPrototypeOf(obj)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "254adebf-8539-4baf-8c02-2851415a1595",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 10282.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "其中target表示的是目标对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "bfc85213-796e-46f0-a187-ec9d0dc29108",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 10602.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Reflect.has(target, propKey)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "00c071fc-7ae4-4126-b733-6b4025e640bc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 10442.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "作用是判断属性是否在对象中",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "88d88923-6c55-4f32-9d5f-7dfa9e9e1a3c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 10602.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "等同于执行propKey in target",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7e739051-66e0-4e59-8f83-3d82a217af63",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 10762.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "其中target表示的是目标对象，propKey表示的是判断的属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7136a91a-02dd-43dd-bb8a-cf66ea382526",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 11082.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Reflect.isExtensible(target)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "18ea2178-b162-4683-9804-a94950648f89",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 10922.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "作用是判断对象是否可扩展",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "739260dd-a7c7-46db-9ece-d7ed81914f3f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 11082.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "等同于执行Object.isExtensible()函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c85980de-3e64-46ed-adec-2b2e839e6d85",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 11242.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "其中target表示的是目标对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "308a2f6c-0724-4410-87c4-9d2c9a8c4e28",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 11562.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Reflect.ownKeys(target)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7819619b-c27c-45f3-b75d-9b7bdfaa073a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 11402.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "作用是获取对象的所有属性，包括Symbol属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8352bab8-22bb-4f4a-bb01-efc3ec2e6cb4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 11562.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "等同于Object.getOwnPropertyNames与Object.getOwnPropertySymbols之和",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "035ebecb-4e6e-405f-9387-16281eccf76e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 11722.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "其中target表示的是目标对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae9e719-a6e5-4234-9aa6-54360953fceb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 12042.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Reflect.preventExtensions(target)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ffa128b6-86e7-4a39-b512-d01ad2b015ed",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 11882.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "作用是让一个对象变得不可扩展",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "854b0bcc-cad0-404a-8442-ef2eb2b03a30",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 12042.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "等同于执行Object.preventExtensions()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "227e4320-a022-4dec-9fa8-cedd141c956e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 12202.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "其中target表示的是目标对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f92cbb51-87f5-4d04-a640-9e3f39abb14f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 12522.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Reflect.set(target, propKey, value, receiver)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4282e1d3-05c0-45de-98dd-914f49ceda75",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 12362.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "作用是设置某个属性值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "757b2341-b1af-4974-afc8-427c2814519f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 12522.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "等同于执行target[propKey] = value",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e43394b1-5b70-4bb0-bfeb-b8d3531c60be",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 12682.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "其中target表示的是目标对象，propKey表示的是待设置的属性，value表示的是设置属性的具体值，receiver表示函数中this绑定的对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "bd65d672-a0d0-4216-b7f1-1773d6d29be8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 13002.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Reflect.setPrototypeOf(target, newProto)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4e0644ca-07cf-4e74-9deb-2aa70affca64",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 12842.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "作用是设置对象的原型prototype",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "2402a137-2471-47f9-bb60-710347f9f1ff",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 13002.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "等同于执行Object.setPrototypeOf(target, newProto)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "07f5c8e8-fef8-4ebb-b36a-29ac6c02efc7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 13162.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "其中target表示的是目标对象，newProto表示的是新的原型对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "da3db276-d2c1-4eb4-9b6b-48e7e85c5a35",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 13522.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Reflect与传统写法的区别",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a24857d3-868d-4d37-8568-947cdf3e2c56",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 13402.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Reflect.apply(target, thisArg, args)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5a1ea26e-a7a3-48dc-bc54-f8068c151e26",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 13322.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "找出数组里的最大元素",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f50020b6-445d-46df-9ea2-54399d5e0db8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 13322.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "// 查找一个数字数组里面的最大元素\nconst arr = [1, 3, 5, 7];\n\nlet max;\n\n// ES6\n\nmax = Reﬂect.apply(Math.max, null, arr);\n\nconsole.log(max);  // 7\n\n// ES5\n\nmax = Math.max.apply(null, arr);\n\nconsole.log(max); // 7\n\nmax = Function.prototype.apply.call(Math.max, null, arr);\n\nconsole.log(max); // 7",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d09328f7-463d-45dd-a3b1-af5ab512c586",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 13482.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "截取字符串中的一部分值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "086e5f12-adef-47f5-b3b6-f3fcf27456cc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 13482.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "// 截取字符串的一部分\nlet str = 'hello, world';\n\nlet newStr;\n\n// ES6\n\nnewStr = Reﬂect.apply(String.prototype.slice, str, [2, 8]);\n\nconsole.log(newStr); // llo，w\n\n// ES5\n\nnewStr = str.slice(2, 8);\n\nconsole.log(newStr); // llo，w\n\nnewStr = String.prototype.slice.apply(str, [2, 8]);\n\nconsole.log(newStr); // llo，w",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0dae4968-7948-41c8-b599-12a0acbe26ae",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 13642.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Reflect.defineProperty(target, propKey, attributes)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6cf50855-13bd-49aa-bf89-f1563831ce65",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 13642.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Reflect.defineProperty()函数与Object.defineProperty()函数的主要区别在于返回值，如果设置失败，Object.defineProperty()函数会抛出一个异常，而Reflect.defineProperty()函数会返回“false”",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4d229ac3-2005-48ba-b207-ed4dca82e94b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 13802.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Reflect 和 Proxy",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "059dafc3-0531-4c6c-94b9-a6d07a18fc12",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 13802.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "ES6在设计的时候就将Reflect对象和Proxy对象绑定在一起了，Reflect对象的函数与Proxy对象的函数一一对应，因此在Proxy对象中调用Reflect对象对应的函数是一个明智的选择",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "df1ec927-89bf-43f7-9533-209d98973e0e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1310.3662298828126,
      "y": 13962.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Promise",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "57b29e71-977b-4b50-9571-556854b4b82a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 13962.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "https://www.yuque.com/u25370234/cwg1kg/tngttyazcg57c2mq",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e8709681-aaf7-4136-973e-6ce9ddd11fe6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1310.3662298828126,
      "y": 14780.653491883959,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Iterator",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d26de1ff-095c-4841-8ed9-a4b392d5ca58",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 14202.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "概述",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a06e1e37-760d-446b-960d-992811579c75",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 14122.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Iterator称为遍历器，是ES6为不同数据结构遍历所新增的统一访问接口",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4cab17ad-2fe8-4ef6-8213-dc2e4c19362b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 14282.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "一个合法的Iterator接口都会具有一个next()函数，在遍历的过程中，依次调用next()函数，返回一个带有value和done属性的对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6cc3d7f1-40f6-41b3-a1eb-fba9a83d9b5f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 14282.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "value值表示当前遍历到的值，done值表示迭代是否结束，true表示迭代完成，Iterator执行结束；false表示迭代未完成，继续执行next()函数，进入下一轮遍历中，直到done值为true",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9fb0a07a-e934-4928-8454-3bd067895cad",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 14602.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "作用",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "2d8f88cf-f250-4174-b707-91ac086c8292",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 14442.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "为任何部署了Iterator接口的数据结构提供统一的访问机制",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "882db9ef-a046-4493-b059-2de86f002b19",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 14602.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "使得数据结构的成员能够按照某种次序排列",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "bb7ed32f-e9fc-4171-ac10-d13148a88e50",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 14762.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "使得数据结构的成员能够按照某种次序排列",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "62c84208-3567-4711-ab02-acbe18d48c68",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 15536.209047439514,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "默认Iterator接口",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "305f05b0-9581-47df-8a62-ac8c5cf491a0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 14922.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "只有部署了Iterator接口的数据结构才能使用for...of遍历",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "805301a4-2fdf-4843-9afa-93b10c0eecb7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 14922.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "对象类型的数据使用for...of循环时，会抛出异常，表示对象不支持使用for...of循环",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "192ea3bb-a9d4-419f-a2cf-d118eb272880",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 15482.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "原生具备Iterator接口的数据结构",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b2cce121-be47-4f2c-8f9c-718666745627",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 15082.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Array",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "99f4914c-e1e1-4d8c-b6e6-55bcae7ec04b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 15242.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Map",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "40d9391b-16b1-471d-998d-bd8645719111",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 15402.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Set",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "eab6608d-69ae-4083-b570-a29c590e63f8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 15562.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "String",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a9eb0184-4aed-4298-a49c-4dd8fd58f7de",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 15722.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Arguments",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6164db15-10f1-4a46-9985-bda8cc0f3248",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 15882.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "NodeList",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0c0c00e4-f89e-4971-b94f-be28772ea2ea",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 16202.87571410618,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "添加Iterator接口",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "605acced-b47e-4321-b3ff-2a935bce52d2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 16042.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Iterator接口是部署在Symbol.iterator属性上的，它是一个函数，因此我们只需要对特定的数据结构加上Symbol.iterator属性即可",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7c789674-1ee0-4c64-9d34-6e9f5c980f1d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 16202.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在Symbol.iterator属性对应的函数中一定要返回一个带有next()函数的对象，在next()函数中需要返回带有value和done属性的对象，以此来满足Iterator的执行过程",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "16bd8a67-14ba-47d1-8ea0-58205703814b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 16362.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "举例",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5765ca01-735b-483e-9353-80a4e28196e2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 16362.875714106181,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "function Person(name, age) {\n    this.name = name;\n\n    this.age = age;\n\n}\n\n// 在原型中添加[Symbol.iterator]属性\n\nPerson.prototype[Symbol.iterator] = function () {\n\n    // 设置变量，记录遍历的次数\n\n    let count = 0;\n\n    // 通过Object.keys()函数获取实例自身的所有属性\n\n   let propArr = Object.keys(this);\n\n    return {\n\n        next: function () {\n\n            // 每执行一次遍历，count值加1\n\n            // 当count值小于属性的长度时，表示仍然可以遍历，设置done值为false\n\n            if (count < propArr.length) {\n\n                let index = count++;\n\n                return {\n\n                    value: propArr[index],\n\n                    done: false\n\n                };\n\n            } else {\n\n                // 当count值等于属性的长度时，遍历结束，设置done值为true\n\n                return {\n\n                    value: undeﬁned,\n\n                    done: true\n\n                }\n\n            }\n\n        }\n\n    }\n\n};\n\nconst person = new Person('kingx', 12);\n\nfor (let key of person) {\n\n    console.log(key, ':', person[key]);\n\n}",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "fea0d042-84a5-4ba7-ba01-db9beb22a807",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1310.3662298828126,
      "y": 17018.87571410618,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "for...of",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "236b9d33-b909-4bee-9758-8c91405f0c39",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 16522.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "数组结构使用for...of循环",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "870be325-8f58-4027-8a00-1d7f4e45ccd0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 16522.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "返回数组中的每个值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e781861d-fa25-4775-89e3-9da8fe484b2d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 16682.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Set数据结构使用for...of循环",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1aa17a48-a7b9-4f7a-a927-7af928e10f36",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 16682.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "返回Set中的每个值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "58cf85e0-2200-47eb-849e-8e26a5f8cdba",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 16842.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Map数据结构使用for...of循环",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "08452d0d-e70e-48fb-9323-6ae434da8fcf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 16842.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "会将Map中的每个键和对应的值组合成一个数组进行返回",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "81c46df3-25ec-4010-b8b0-26d6d3880da6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 17162.87571410618,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "特定函数的返回值使用for...of循环",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "509f3be2-ad2c-4b2d-aaac-0a17494f7fb5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 17002.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Object.entries()函数：返回一个遍历器对象，由键、值构成的对象数组",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "fbfa1cd7-74b1-4b21-a064-0b0fa6fb164f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 17162.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Object.keys()函数：返回一个遍历器对象，由所有的键构成的数组",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ebb239a1-6b85-4a3c-a5cc-a3325e072390",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 17322.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Object.values()函数：返回一个遍历器对象，由所有的值构成的数组",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "13b48147-91cd-40c6-8ef9-4d82b9c7c9cd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 17882.87571410618,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "与其他循环方式的比较",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "78ea2211-374f-4f38-b8cd-0b2568b2acdb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 17562.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "forEach的问题",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "bdde5e68-b702-473c-9d93-f9acb4899487",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 17482.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "无法跳出循环，不支持break和continue关键字",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f267782a-453f-46e8-ac31-7ede44619754",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 17482.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果使用了break或continue关键字则会抛出异常",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9d638747-b467-46e3-a476-6c504db97d4a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 17642.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "使用return关键字会跳过当前循环，但仍会执行后续的循环",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "11380dfc-40b8-46d1-82a3-c26741ec7eaf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 17882.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "for...in的问题",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "89b056db-2622-48ea-853f-14a67bd36db6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 17802.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在使用for...in循环遍历数组时，返回的键是字符串表示的数组的索引，如“0”“1”“2”，并不是数组项的值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "53e7592a-2ddc-4845-bd2f-0be2b2f69b2b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 17962.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "通过手动给数组实例添加的属性，同样会被遍历出来，而事实上我们并不希望这些额外的属性被遍历出来",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "43c86f6a-4b60-4013-9de8-28c9c0f2bd98",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 18202.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "for...of",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "13f20a29-5b50-4b00-8c30-2e1077782a14",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 18122.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "和for...in循环有同样的语法，但没有for...in循环的缺点，遍历数组时，返回的是数组每项的值，而且给数组实例新增的属性并不会被遍历出来",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4c5a15f5-d8f1-43ad-8ab4-b85bb1051430",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 18282.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在for...of循环中，可以使用break、continue和return等关键字",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b0924039-6a9f-407e-b24a-2eb2c3c458b4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1310.3662298828126,
      "y": 20459.54238077285,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Generator",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8b94cdfb-f7fa-4738-bad0-f95ddf4bd52c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 19696.209047439515,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "定义",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4050d1f9-70b3-449d-9031-5066969ac12a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 18602.87571410618,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "概述",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c245865c-6fcd-43ce-a76c-a7e51e3202c2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 18442.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Generator()函数是ES6提供的一种异步编程解决方案",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e0f01f1f-22d5-4a72-bb3f-471e41c7e055",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 18602.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Generator()函数本质上也是一个函数，调用方法也与普通函数相同",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "98477a61-f86a-4b47-abb6-c4c745d02e4f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 18762.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Generator()函数从语法上可以理解为是一个状态机，函数内部维护多个状态，函数执行的结果返回一个部署了Iterator接口的对象，通过这个对象可以依次获取Generator()函数内部的每一个状态",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0d676e43-60bc-4884-8076-8741396b0e49",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 19082.87571410618,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "特征",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1cc6aeec-9c65-4365-813a-157235a6f633",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 18922.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "function关键字与函数名之间有一个星号（*）",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "094380c9-5d74-4ada-adbb-678eda0b15a1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 19082.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "函数体内部使用yield关键字来定义不同的内部状态",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "2175d272-31a9-4422-a876-8799806058ba",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 19242.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "返回一个部署了Iterator接口的对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3169a2ef-8da2-4e02-b766-28f44f36a8c1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 19242.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "直到调用next()函数时，才开始从函数头部向下执行，直到遇到yield表达式或者return语句才会停止",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bffb543-224c-4ff7-bdb1-04a8aa69a97e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 19562.87571410618,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Generator()函数中的yield表达式与next()函数的关系",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8ed4573f-6379-4357-9af3-f507a6c38411",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 19402.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "next()函数的返回值是一个具有value和done属性的对象，next()函数调用后，如果遇到yield表达式，就会暂停后面的操作，并将yield表达式执行的结果作为value值进行返回，此时done属性的值为false",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "aa83ceb4-ab17-4b00-aa8b-cc45066cc075",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 19562.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "当再次执行next()函数时，会再继续往下执行，直到遇到下一个yield表达式",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4592ba99-5254-4c4a-a42d-2ca6db707921",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 19722.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "当所有的yield语句执行完毕时，会直接运行至函数末尾，如果有return语句，将return语句的表达式值作为value值返回；如果没有return语句，则value以undefined值进行返回，这两种情况下的done属性的值都为true，遍历结束",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d4754f48-fb39-4574-8f46-c1191ec69250",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 20042.87571410618,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "return与yield语句都能将后面的表达式作为next()函数的返回值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5f38fd7d-73c8-418a-b7a8-d48e5ebfad1b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 19882.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "当遇到yield语句时，程序的执行会暂停，而return语句却不会，一旦return语句执行，整个函数执行结束，后面的yield语句都会失效",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f40575ef-4845-44b9-becc-92c3d0829a61",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 20042.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "return语句如果没有返回值，那么next()函数的返回值为“{ value:undefined,done: true }”。\nyield语句如果没有接表达式，next()函数的返回值中value值同样为“undefined”，而done属性的值为“false”",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4a2aca6e-e97b-43cd-a9ae-77685c94bc80",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 20202.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Generator()函数能有多个yield语句，但是只能有一个return语句",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "eee34638-f1e8-4031-b540-78ce1d0a1087",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 20362.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "yield语句本身没有返回值，如果将其赋给一个变量，则该变量的值为undefined",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3d51b46a-a7e0-4614-bc36-47b1e669cb06",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 20362.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果我们想要使用上一轮yield表达式的结果，则需要借助next()函数，next()函数携带的参数可以作为上一轮yield表达式的返回值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "cb7a60b0-0a6a-4001-a4ce-b35961375ef8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 20522.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "for...of循环遍历Generator()函数的返回值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0c0fe3f0-7896-43b9-9e46-a747b4dddce6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 20522.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Generator()函数的返回值是一个部署了Iterator接口的对象，刚好可以使用for...of循环进行遍历，并且不需要手动调用next()函数，遍历的结果就是yield表达式的返回值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "12551b35-c828-48e9-9115-2a1d3a59670c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 21222.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "注意事项",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "82b419ae-8558-4fc9-9a6e-21fc19f3dff9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 20682.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "默认情况下不能使用new关键字",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "268ddd5c-6b90-46a4-b7e1-c43ac975a0e4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 20682.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Generator()函数并不是构造函数，在默认情况下，不能使用new关键字。如果使用，则会抛出TypeError异常",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0ade956d-fc09-4d56-9850-93b1b24a8715",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 20842.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "yield表达式会延迟执行",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d423977e-ca42-4862-a3ac-865c09b61dc1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 20842.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在Generator()函数中，yield表达式只有在调用next()函数时才会去执行，因此起到了延迟执行的效果",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "75e87ec8-af27-467e-a717-da82f0b3e143",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 21002.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "yield表达式只能在Generator()函数中调用",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0191f2d6-017d-4644-89d9-8123653421d2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 21002.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果出现在普通函数或者匿名函数中则会抛出语法异常",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a9b6a031-bd0d-46be-bfa6-b00edb6c74c2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 21242.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "yield表达式需要小括号括起来",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "09b0807d-ee4d-4ac6-aae9-d614a93b9d75",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 21162.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "当一个yield表达式出现在其他表达式中时，需要用小括号将yield表达式括起来，否则会抛出语法异常",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a0fbef28-cc29-4287-ae3a-acf9c9fb5e66",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 21322.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "function* demo() {\n    console.log('Hello' + yield 123); // 抛出SyntaxError异常\n\n    console.log('Hello' + (yield 123)); // 正确\n\n}",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "67b9066c-1c29-4bf6-8413-aeaeba093bd4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 21602.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Generator()函数中的this特殊处理",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4cd470be-0db9-4a4a-984c-1708875bbbfa",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 21482.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在默认情况下，不能使用new关键字生成Generator的实例，因此Generator()函数中的this是无效的",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "fa9ed4c3-89d2-4f0f-8948-4c1c3f283ee9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 21722.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果既想使用Generator()函数的特性，又想使用this的特性，那该怎么做呢？",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9f1758e7-ec2b-488d-9223-7e5d8f5f19f4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 21642.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "使用call()函数改变Generator()函数的执行主体为Generator()函数的prototype属性，使得this指向原型属性，这样就可以访问到原型上添加的属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7c15b59b-e0c4-45c2-8b3c-133980a9adf9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 21802.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "function* testGenerator() {\n    this.name = 'kingx';\n\n    yield 'hello';\n\n    yield 'world';\n\n}\n\n// 使用call()函数改变执行主体为testGenerator的prototype属性\n\nlet t = testGenerator.call(testGenerator.prototype);\n\nt.next();\n\nconsole.log(t.name);  // kingx",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c6559065-e074-4ca8-a1ec-db48aa12564c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 21962.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Generator()函数嵌套使用",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a45ca014-658d-43e0-8618-b2ea9b05b4e2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 21962.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果在一个Generator()函数内部调用另一个Generator()函数，那么在不使用yield*语句的情况下，需要手动遍历上一个Generator()函数，并在遍历完成后进入当前Generator()函数中",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8e181a5a-5a43-4440-a299-78a559e21b42",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 21962.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "function* fn1() {\n    yield 'test1';\n\n}\n\nfunction* fn2() {\n\n    yield 'test2';\n\n    // 调用另外一个Generator()函数，使用yield*关键字\n\n    yield* fn1();\n\n    yield 'test3';\n\n}\n\nlet f = fn2();\n\nfor (let key of f) {\n\n    console.log(key);\n\n}",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "30c75187-0163-4ca4-aeb3-037d843b04aa",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1310.3662298828126,
      "y": 23152.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Class",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f353ca55-245c-4a9f-8a6f-1a96568e5661",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 22582.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "基本用法",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b328add9-ab4e-46e1-9c80-5482a47ef266",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 22122.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "使用class关键字定义类的名称，然后在类的constructor构造函数中定义实例属性，原型属性在class内部直接声明并赋值，原型函数的声明与构造函数处于同一层级，并且省略function关键字",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b5b3f2c6-65cf-4f3a-841a-3d41c4fe8e94",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 22362.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "constructor()函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4cbd860f-278f-4bae-87ab-9364207ce118",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 22282.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "constructor()函数是一个类必须具有的函数，可以手动添加，如果没有手动添加，则会自动隐式添加一个空的constructor()函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e03227bd-6db2-4ce5-8674-121eea48f640",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 22442.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "constructor()函数默认会返回当前对象的实例，即默认的this指向，我们可以手动修改返回值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f1df0c53-e2c7-4536-8dcd-95a901e9d1d6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 22682.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "静态属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f09c9a48-9c30-42b4-9920-7b9d9149130e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 22602.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "静态属性和函数同样存在于类内部，使用static关键字修饰时，静态属性和函数无法被实例访问，只能通过类自身使用",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1b0772ae-76ae-40f3-aa65-ffe44426bb34",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 22762.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "静态函数中的this指向的是类本身，而不是类的实例，也正因为静态函数和实例函数中的this是隔离的，所以同一个类中可以存在函数名相同的静态函数和实例函数。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3a6773f3-a2ef-4360-85e0-64da86e75481",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 23162.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "注意点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "bdd19d7d-eb00-4266-b541-f08353e44093",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 22922.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "只能与new关键字配合使用",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "eae7df45-bc90-4615-a421-28dd8521835f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 22922.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "直接以函数的方式调用类时，会抛出一个异常",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5fd1a90b-0320-4255-8ad8-f294c27aa528",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 23082.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不存在变量提升",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "45894206-12da-4113-82a8-4d78d71f3d98",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 23082.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "class定义的类同样不存在变量提升，因此如果在定义类之前去使用它，会抛出引用异常",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6d74a2a3-71f8-47b8-8fb6-565bab2d310d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 23242.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在类中声明函数时，不要加function关键字",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6fa7b1ac-e3a9-4776-8df1-a13d875a58f4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 23242.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在类中声明函数时，不要加function关键字，否则会抛出语法异常",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "2b44d795-08f1-4434-99fb-1562e12442bd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 23402.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "this指向会发生变化",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "320242fd-be9f-4f1e-8e42-a351cb2cb315",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 23402.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "类内部的this默认指向的是类的实例，在调用实例函数时，一定要注意this的指向性问题。如果单独使用实例函数时，this的指向会发生变化，很容易带来一定的问题",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c04f1d0c-b9d4-4266-9feb-11b016dbce95",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 23722.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "继承",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4e4327fb-945f-4b4f-90a6-cc29a4e0b0b3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 23562.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "ES6新增了extends关键字，可以快速实现类的继承",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9dd8389f-a630-43d9-9d85-0b63d14bc56b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 23562.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "使用extends关键字不仅可以继承自定义的类，还可以继承原生的内置构造函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "514b161f-063d-44d9-8824-f4bc487c62a1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 23722.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在子类的constructor构造函数中，需要首先调用super()函数执行父类的构造函数，再执行子类的函数修饰this",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8dd602f3-db1c-4a3b-a103-783088df0060",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 23882.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "父类的静态函数无法被实例继承，但可以被子类继承。子类在访问时同样是通过本身去访问，而不是通过子类实例去访问",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0bfaf121-8518-4cca-8a97-7f82136fe26b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1310.3662298828126,
      "y": 26150.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Module",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "af2c7783-85a5-410d-b9ad-791a2234c7df",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 24362.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "概述",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "13e2e8d8-2df1-421c-b401-e49ceee6d3f8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 24202.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "与commonJs的区别",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0371e61b-2ba8-47a1-9b34-c0e9afc13fb3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 24042.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "CommonJS在运行时完成模块的加载，而ES6模块是在编译时完成模块的加载，效率要更高。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ff98308f-4f01-471f-99ca-21f47a86e48e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 24202.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "CommonJS模块是对象，而ES6模块可以是任何数据类型，通过export命令指定输出的内容，并通过import命令引入即可",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3f21a4d4-0971-4fb6-8b68-fb854ae344b0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 24362.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "CommonJS模块会在require加载时完成执行，而ES6的模块是动态引用，只在执行时获取模块中的值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c46aea42-7b59-42ba-bcad-c7c05d9eaad2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 24522.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "ES6模块核心的内容在于export命令和import命令的使用，两者相辅相成，共同为模块化服务",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7c2ffe87-750f-4538-9938-51b959ba65b2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 25062.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "export",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "651ba508-7698-4d7e-824a-0929f3c5d7bd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 24682.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "export命令用于定义模块对外输出的内容，任何你想通过外部文件进行访问的内容，只需要通过export关键字就可以完成。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c36b6da1-3884-41b9-bcde-654448afd13a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 24922.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "export的是接口，而不是值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7af29819-9d29-4041-b161-ef737ccd1597",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 24922.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不能直接通过export输出变量值，而是需要对外提供接口，必须与模块内部的变量建立一一对应的关系",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "94fa123a-f710-4a27-a48a-75230bef8bbd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 24842.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "错误写法",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "868676f1-2a23-4d42-aaca-101b5eb02a1b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 24842.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "let obj = {};\nlet a = 1;\n\nfunction foo() {}\n\nexport obj;  // 错误写法\n\nexport a;  // 错误写法\n\nexport foo; // 错误写法",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9b56c883-e678-4b62-b6de-5631dd2ee76b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 25002.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "正确写法",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b7523e30-972d-47f5-b683-7c56e5db03b3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 25002.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "let obj = {};\nfunction foo() {}\n\nexport let a = 1; // 正确写法\n\nexport {obj}; // 正确写法\n\nexport {foo}; // 正确写法",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "46efa2cc-5bd0-45b3-a507-f82530b990a6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 25162.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "export值的实时性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "70adc596-e993-4f4e-b36d-980faca31169",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 25162.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "export对外输出的接口，在外部模块引用时，是实时获取的，并不是import那个时刻的值。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "bf38b3b6-6e65-4f9f-bab6-d6e8ece561eb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 25482.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "常见用法",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "48786660-53fc-4d83-b7d6-39d08875a40e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 25322.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "使用as关键字设置别名",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d1992f02-b864-46ee-b624-f85f2d2d4d77",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 25482.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "相同变量名只能够export一次",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9e6c894d-4f16-42e5-8429-3bddfffd350d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 25642.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "尽量统一export",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "417afa8d-8a6f-403d-bc35-36a574537f65",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 25642.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "文件export的内容有很多，建议都放在文件末尾处统一进行export，这样对export的内容能一目了然",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "47f1ac0b-e19e-4dc8-a457-9fa287842ceb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 26442.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "import",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "21748054-61f4-45db-b933-846d6b3f4fff",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 25882.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "定义",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c99df8bb-f36c-4e00-a898-8c2c37e182c6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 25802.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "一个模块中使用export命令导出的内容，通过import命令可以引到另一个模块中，两者可以相互配合使用",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7af7baeb-d33c-480b-8c76-4994145437cf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 25962.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果想要在HTML页面中使用import命令，需要在script标签上使用代码type=\"module\"",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d997e09f-30c1-4f81-a847-3e16be173843",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 26442.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "特性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8a033f6c-5ab8-4556-968f-64a5c1eded66",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 26122.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "与export的变量名相同",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "470d0ec3-c7e9-413b-8876-eed9d0b63fbe",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 26122.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "import命令引入的变量需要放在一个大括号里，括成对象的形式，而且import的变量名必须与export的变量名一致",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c010b8c8-d65e-42a7-8e59-34129569ac62",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 26282.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "相同变量名的值只能import一次",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "94da14a9-a6d8-4bd5-a4a9-2280f58b647e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 26442.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "import命令具有提升的效果",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "87e7e76b-a802-433b-8b8a-55441a3df3a5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 26442.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "本质上是因为import是在编译期运行的，在执行输出代码之前已经执行了import语句",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c13ad776-3865-4034-a1a3-103c90465a6c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 26602.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "多次import时，只会一次加载",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ed7e1bac-0203-4d54-918a-d18b27ca04c8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 26602.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "每个模块只加载一次，每个JS文件只执行一次，如果在同一个文件中多次import相同的模块，则只会执行一次模块文件，后续直接从内存读取",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ec584597-6bb9-443e-9747-c7398b1977dd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 26762.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "import的值本身是只读的，不可修改",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e6c621b5-d405-466e-9d2b-97e3087ec403",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 26762.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "使用import命令导入的值，如果是基本数据类型，那么它们的值是不可以修改的，相当于一个const常量；如果是引用数据类型的值，那么它们的引用本身是不能修改的，只能修改引用对应的值本身",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "cd6412fb-da52-44c6-a959-38071b30de1e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 27002.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "常见用法",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a986eae8-779b-4410-8736-0cabfa0f9465",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 26922.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "设置引入变量的别名",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "2409dedf-c811-49fe-80b4-1f463e85ee57",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 26922.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "使用as关键字为变量设置别名，可以用于解决上一部分中相同变量名import一次的问题",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "825d5c25-27a5-480e-ade4-df53a4e76125",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 27082.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "模块整体加载",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a3f0bd85-0bc7-4d78-bfad-8f399385aae5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 27082.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "当我们需要加载整个模块的内容时，可以使用星号（*）配合as关键字指定一个对象，通过对象去访问各个输出值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "529bbc2b-ee5c-4b2b-87ad-4477c2fe98fd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 27322.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "export default",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b48e7302-59ab-43a7-ae12-f5726526174c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 27242.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "一个文件只有一个export default语句",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e017b0df-3d81-41e7-b975-95ee346633d5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 27402.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "import的内容不需要使用大括号括起来",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5c0b2435-668e-4d78-b8a1-2df1188079e1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 27562.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Module加载的实质",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3ce69d80-26ea-4e71-8d52-cf14120beab3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 27562.875714106183,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "ES6模块的运行机制是这样的：当遇到import命令时，不会立马去执行模块，而是生成一个动态的模块只读引用，等到需要用到时，才去解析引用对应的值",
      "color": "5"
    }
  ],
  "edges": [
    {
      "id": "7b009bf2e9e1438680b03912568ef767",
      "fromNode": "cbed35ae-b714-4cac-9a62-3dc607391d4e",
      "fromSide": "right",
      "toNode": "0337930b-f319-4a6d-a3d4-c9f969466135",
      "toSide": "left"
    },
    {
      "id": "aade63327f034556866db1db8e88fe16",
      "fromNode": "0337930b-f319-4a6d-a3d4-c9f969466135",
      "fromSide": "right",
      "toNode": "35e29116-e6e4-4324-9766-b2ef7cfc340b",
      "toSide": "left"
    },
    {
      "id": "d4588b7331ed49eaa6e01ab97a6d46b9",
      "fromNode": "35e29116-e6e4-4324-9766-b2ef7cfc340b",
      "fromSide": "right",
